I"—<h1 id="being-distracted-by-setting">Being distracted by setting:</h1>

<p>If your attention is divided, your ability to listen well will be affected. To remove this barrier, make sure you are in a setting where you will not be interrupted and remove your phone or other distractions within he room.</p>

<h1 id="being-distracted-by-your-thoughts">Being distracted by your thoughts:</h1>

<p>When you listen, it is very natural to become distracted and preoccupied by your own personal narrative and reactions to what you are hearing. By becoming aware of when you become lost in your own thoughts you can return to your awareness back to the present moment.</p>
